{"type": "article", "id": 33409, "title": "Karl Lagerfeld也要开酒店，以及，推荐一个新的皮衣品牌 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-10-18T02:57:49Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 253, "name": "LINE"}, {"id": 17698, "name": "购物季"}, {"id": 33826, "name": "2016 上海时装周"}, {"id": 34026, "name": "中东零售市场"}, {"id": 984, "name": "Coty"}, {"id": 34027, "name": "Elephant Blanc"}, {"id": 34028, "name": "NASASEASONS"}, {"id": 2961, "name": "Karl Lagerfeld"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 39, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161018101423inBjpwMz8lC25foQ.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><b><a href=\"http://www.vogue.com/13492906/karl-lagerfeld-hotels-resorts-restaurants-travel-news/\" rel=\"nofollow\">老佛爷 Karl Lagerfeld 也要进军酒店业</a></b> | 继 Giorgio Armani、Bulgari、Versace 之后，时装设计大师 Karl Lagerfeld 也要进军酒店业了。目前，他正在筹划自己的国际酒店品牌 Karl Lagerfeld Hotels &amp; Resorts，已经和帮助品牌进军酒店业的授权平台 Brandmark Collective BV 签署了长期授权协议。&nbsp;<br></p><p><a href=\"https://www.businessoffashion.com/articles/news-analysis/coty-to-acquire-hairstyling-appliance-maker-ghd-for-511-million\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Coty 要花 5.11 亿美元，买下一家英国美发器材公司</b></a> | GHD 是一家来自英国的美发器材公司，在过去的三年里，公司业务实现了 30% 的增长，2016 财年的营收为 1.78 亿英镑。日化巨头 Coty 在买下宝洁的 41 个品牌之后，斥资 5.11 亿美元买 GHD，以扩展 Coty 在专业美发领域的业务。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/retail-news/trends-analysis/consumer-spending-patterns-retail-10676997/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>年底购物季，中东零售市场或将面临下滑</b></a> | 美国 RSM 会计事务所的首席经济学家 Joe Brusuelas 指出，由于消费者更加青睐网络购物，中东零售市场在这个购物季将会面临下滑。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p class=\"\">上海时装周上的 Pider BB 是来自香港的童装品牌，在这次的秀场上，他们带来了&nbsp;normcore、fairy tales、classic 三个系列。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161018080257GdwHn1VKv463jq8P.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161018080256ExabHT3NDjlywv62.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161018080257IGLSU1Fnu3VwRMJg.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161018080257rifXB68pOCHEanxJ.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161018080258lQYhd6bR8Mj3aWwp.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161018080258weTFHuRSk8Ca0PjQ.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161018080259UkTByQargnbSe92q.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161018080259NLCsq51Hkgi0SDGU.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>喜欢民族味道的服装的话，这个日本的品牌值得一看。品牌 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/10/elephant-blanc-2017-ss-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">Elephant Blanc</a> 是设计师渡边康二于 2008 年秋冬创立的。渡边康二从传统的洋服剪裁出发，从东南亚的民族风格中汲取灵感，在简约的剪裁中加以恰到好处的民族元素，呈现出一种淡然的民族味道。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610180910415HqzjdgGemyu0XfP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161018091050CUnlQz2L40wveVJE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161018091058kX39t4sbnBFfSv2J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161018091059CdDge0jStHVl6zn8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161018091059zcnZfjGaEvK8mw03.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161018091059WBJskgfx8iyhLK2H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161018091106LJ5CrPIBTRmfoA12.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>作为贴纸界的 icon，<a href=\"http://popbee.com/lifestyle/food/e-g-sain-line-friends/#\" rel=\"nofollow\">Line Friends</a> 最近又与台湾伴手礼品牌“一之乡”合作，推出了一系列不仅有着好看的礼盒包装，连食物上都印着卡通图案的联名款产品。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161018091200Ee4AjLIUVQhas2xz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610180912145twljfWJk4U8XxZ1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161018091214h2m1fAnyHUKtLM8d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161018091214Ia6Zgmeuc2qsCNKJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161018091215rZGWKuvYeDV7l0PL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161018091220NCx197vF5jhzkrsT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">NASASEASONS 是由 19 岁法国年轻小伙 Millinsky 与几个朋友一起创立的新晋街头时尚品牌，三年前推出了连蕾哈娜都喜欢的 Dad Hat。最近，这个品牌又发布了它的 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/10/nasaseasons-2016-fall-winter-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">2016 秋冬系列 lookbook</a>。经典的 90 复古元素再度回归，抢眼的标语 I used to miss you，Less heartbroken 依然出彩。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161018091519zjWLrcqIEndSviFZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666369\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161018091530dRsy1OE2cV6qAhrm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666431\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161018091531j9W4OdbHkENDSB71.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666431\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161018091531PxtZgCAX8wqLzrG4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666431\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161018091531ibgf4EFVlmJAqCH7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666431\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161018091531BLHhsuJoQnziOtFc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666431\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161018091531lOKIRi5ejxfPELN8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666431\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161018091537OVbFlqW1Z2ITB0Dw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666431\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">推荐一个来自伦敦的全新皮衣品牌<a href=\"http://popbee.com/fashion/cult-worthy-a-lineutm_/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> A-line</a>。这个品牌由英国设计师 Anne-Sophine Kohler 在 2013 年正式推出。每一件来自 A-line 的皮衣都使用了百分百软羊皮，并且有着独特的拼接图案。这种拼接的灵感来自设计师 Kohler，她将一些多余的布料拼接在皮夹克上，形成了 A-line 的标志性风格。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610180918536TzkQEaZ48RmbI3D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610180918461ycbtgYWnm2ASIux.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161018091837BTZeFXpalqSiUuYI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161018091824TwvE0cq5eAUOYfGP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div>"}